# Updater signing private key (Phase 8) — never commit. The matching
# `.pub` file is fine to commit (it's already inlined into tauri.conf.json's
# plugins.updater.pubkey) but the private half must stay out of git; sign
# release builds via TAURI_SIGNING_PRIVATE_KEY_PATH pointed at a securely
# stored copy, not this checked-out file.
updater-signing-key.private
